author: Manoranjan Dash and Huan Liu and Peter Scheuermann and Kian-Lee Tan
title: Fast hierarchical clustering and its validation
window: consists of 10,992 objects in 16 dimensions. There are 10 classes corresponding to digits 0...9. The 16 dimensions are drawn by re-sampling from handwritten digits. Iris dataset has 150 points in 4 dimensions in 3 clusters. Dimensions are sepal length, sepal width, petal length, and petal width. Clusters are Iris Setosa, Iris Versicolour, and Iris Virginia.
